{"tid":2516432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女子拎鉸剪搭港鐵 乘客驚魂","createTime":"2021-05-04T15:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T23:19:12.000Z","uid":38539,"like":47,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd94bcdb188a683de9625a0b1293fa1335d6d33","tid":2516432,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXdKoocET95RjMRhHKQ4s35wyuJFLHPzPq98Cbjmx9Jd4?filename=ONNuvxy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONNuvxy.png&h=2d71e62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上7時許，港鐵荃灣綫列車內，一名白衣女子被發現坐在車廂座位，手上拿着一把鉸剪，並將尖端舉起指向其他乘客，未有其他舉動，附近座位乘客見狀紛紛躲避，並報警求助。警員於太子站上車了解，女子依然沒有其他舉措，情緒也平靜，便將她帶離車廂，並前往就近的旺角警署。暫時女子動機仍待調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/5VYIN36FCFAV7DLRRX6BNWDGN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2F5VYIN36FCFAV7DLRRX6BNWDGN4%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=ad6b0168\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2F5VYIN36FCFAV7DLRRX6BNWDGN4%2F&h=0cce134d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/5VYIN36FCFAV7DLRRX6BNWDGN4/</a>"},{"pid":"e35de0586a1f893994bbb6f03722d52a3f5c544f","tid":2516432,"uid":47021,"like":15,"dislike":102,"score":-87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"咁少事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c723857a040e7dd2ad46f82458678713cee034e","tid":2516432,"uid":38904,"like":108,"dislike":10,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"e35de0586a1f893994bbb6f03722d52a3f5c544f","tid":2516432,"uid":47021,"like":15,"dislike":102,"score":-87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"咁少事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n我哋連登坐喺 taliban isis 隔籬都未驚過"},{"pid":"8dc0f38f81d87ec2b2ab3b9